823
00:34:15,980 --> 00:34:18,380
 Spržene su civilizacije.

824
00:34:18,380 --> 00:34:19,640
 Tad je Mohenđudaro,

825
00:34:19,640 --> 00:34:20,860
 Harapa,

826
00:34:21,820 --> 00:34:22,420
 Lothal,

827
00:34:22,420 --> 00:34:23,860
 to su gradovi

828
00:34:23,860 --> 00:34:25,780
 u civilizaciji

829
00:34:25,780 --> 00:34:26,740
 doline Inde,

830
00:34:26,740 --> 00:34:27,980
 današnja Indija i Pakistan.

831
00:34:27,980 --> 00:34:29,940
 Sprženi pod jako

832
00:34:29,940 --> 00:34:31,280
