836
00:34:37,020 --> 00:34:39,040
 u Indoneziju jednog vulkana.

837
00:34:39,040 --> 00:34:42,060
 Dakle, svaka ta katastrofa

838
00:34:42,060 --> 00:34:43,140
 bi vraćala

839
00:34:43,140 --> 00:34:44,940
 početak,

840
00:34:44,940 --> 00:34:46,260
 bi vraćala na početak

841
00:34:46,260 --> 00:34:48,080
 život na zemlji,

842
00:34:48,080 --> 00:34:49,360
 život čovjeka

843
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:51,220
