847
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:58,400
 A one su upravo i najveće.

848
00:34:58,400 --> 00:35:00,920
 Dakle, u Kini su

849
00:35:00,920 --> 00:35:02,240
 najveće i najstarije.

850
00:35:02,240 --> 00:35:03,860
 U Egiptu su

851
00:35:03,860 --> 00:35:05,080
 najveće i najstarije.

852
00:35:05,080 --> 00:35:06,820
 To čak priznaju

853
00:35:06,820 --> 00:35:07,560
 egiptolozi.

854
00:35:07,560 --> 00:35:08,400
 Oni kažu

855
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:09,640
 po njima

856
00:35:09,640 --> 00:35:10,720
 piramide 3.

857
00:35:10,720 --> 00:35:11,060
 4.

858
00:35:11,060 --> 00:35:11,600
 5.

